\newlabel{fig:dcn-2qubit}{{3}{5}{Two-qubit state in Dimensional Circular Notation. Circles are arranged in a $2 \times 2$ grid with explicit dimensional axes $Q_1$ and $Q_2$, corresponding to the two qubits. Two-qubit DCN: Circles arranged in 2D space with one dimension per qubit}{figure.3}{}}
