\newlabel{fig:cluster-state}{{15}{15}{The cluster state, a 2D square lattice graph state. This is a universal resource for measurement-based quantum computation, where computation proceeds through single-qubit measurements on the entangled cluster. Cluster State: 2D square lattice graph, universal resource for one-way quantum computation}{figure.15}{}}
